Package: anna-daemon
Version: 1.6.0-rc.1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: systemd, adduser, logrotate
Maintainer: Anna Assistant Team <maintainer@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/yourusername/anna-assistant
Description: Anna Assistant - Ethical AI system maintenance daemon
 Anna is an autonomous system assistant that provides ethical, wiki-grounded
 advice for Arch Linux maintenance tasks. Features include:
 .
  - Temporal forecasting with bias detection (Chronos Loop)
  - Mirror audit and self-reflection (Phase 1.6)
  - Advisory-only parameter adjustments (never auto-applied)
  - Append-only audit trail with durability guarantees
  - Conscience sovereignty enforcement
 .
 This package includes:
  - annad: The Anna daemon with RPC server
  - annactl: CLI client for interacting with the daemon
  - Systemd service configuration
  - Logrotate configuration for audit logs
  - AppArmor profile for security isolation
